FBIS4-65104 "drweu092_i_94003" FBIS-WEU-94-092 Daily Report 12 May 1994 FRANCE Balladur Addresses National Assembly on Bosnia Balladur Addresses National Assembly on Bosnia Karadzic Says Release Possibly `Soon' LD1205074994 Paris France-Inter Radio Network in French 0700 GMT 12 May 94 LD1205074994 Paris France-Inter Radio Network French BFN [Text] I have just learned that the 11 French people from the aid organization Premiere Urgence who are being detained in Bosnia could be released soon. This was said this morning by Radovan Karadzic, the Bosnian Serb leader. According to the Bosnian Serb agency SRNA [Serbian News Agency], the release could take place as soon as a legal formula has been found. [passage omitted]
